name: react-native-reliantid-authorize-net
description: `react-native-reliantid-authorize-net` is a package that allows you to: Fetch token by sending `card detail` to `AcceptSDK` for iOS and Android. You need to use this token to get the values of `DATA DESCRIPTOR` and `DATA VALUE` from the token.
author: Peter Machowski <peter@reliantid.com>
